name: Louis Vuitton
user_report:
These blue Louis Vuitton pills are very common nowadays in Israel. 
Before taking it, I checked it with Marquis and the result was OK - dark purple.
I took a half at about 2:30 in a party. I felt nothing in the next hour and only after about 70 minutes I started feeling something very mellow.
Therefore, I took another half, but sadly, it didn't help.
Not only that, it made me tired and not interested in the party, music or the people, and that is very rare for me.

It looks like they filled this pill with a low dose of MDMA and with other unknown stuff.

Overall, I had a bad experience with this pill and wouldn't recommend it to anybody.
description: Blue rounded Louis Vuitton pill

name: Philipp Plein
user_report:
I tested it with Marquise and it turned out dark purple, which means that it has MDxx.

Took a half at a party at about 1:00
it took a bit more than an hour until I started feeling something, which was mellow. At about 2:30 I took another half, hoping that things would get better. However, Unfortunately, It just got worse. I felt heavy and tired and the thing that I mostly wanted is just to sit down. not to dance, not to have fun, just sit down. 
It's the worst pill I ever took. Looks like it has something else in addition to MDMA or maybe the MDMA in it is not from a good and energizing type.

Upon telling my friends about it, 2 of my friends told me that they also tried this pills a few months ago and felt the same, they got tired after taking it and it made them heavy and not fun.

I do not recommend taking this Blue Philip Plein Pill.

name: Tesla
user_report:
Around 8 pm i took the first pill.1 hour passed and felt nothing .

Then i took 2nd one and started waiting.It was around 11 pm when i decided to take the 3rd one.

At 12 am i went to bathroom to take a piss.When i was washing my hands i looked at mirror and i realized that my pupils were dilated as never before.Loved the look of my eyes.

I started watching my pupils in the mirror for a while then I went back into my room for texting my friend.And at that moment i started seeing blue little dots on the letters of my phone's keyboard.

The sad part begins, my friends.
While i was texting my friend i was sitting on my comfortable bean bag chair.And yes you guessed right.I fell asleep.I believe it was around 1 am when i fell asleep.
I have no idea how it happened but i was quite sad that i experienced nothing.

The next morning,felt lot of urge to vomit.But never could.Extremely painful headaches.Severe stomach cramps.Had really hard time to eat or drink.I had some white spots on my tongue.Which hurt like crazy when it came in contact with food/drink.

One of the weirdest thing was,when i moved my eyes left and right quickly.i felt my heartbeat literally on my face.It was quiet fun actually i kept doing it a lot.

All these physical side effects lasted about 36 hours.
After that i started experiencing the comedown from hell.For 3 days i could not even think about anything positive at all.I had really nice things going on in my life but thinking about those made everything worse.

I dont know what to rate this as,hope you guys can help.
Cheers !
description: I consumed all 3 of them.I do feel a warning is necessary for these because of the comedown.

name: Mario Bullet Bill
user_report:
8:30 pm 
Took 1 pill while resting next to the pool. It was not dark,you could still see the blue sky. (2 dudes)
9:00 pm
Started to see moving wavy patterns on the floor.The sounds of bugs and water in the pool were absolutely incredible.I could hear the bugs really close to me.The colors of trees and flowers were enhanced like an instagram filter.
10:00 pm
We went home to listen to some music.Drank some OJ and took another one.We went out to the garden and sat down to feel the earth.It was around 12 am when we started to slowly comedown but we went back home and took the 3rd one.With hot coffee.Saw lots of abstract visuals.I saw lots of numbers on the walls.


It lasted until 3 am.At 3:30 am we took another one but it was a different pill.(Green Grenade,Ps:This pill also gave the same reaction on Marquis test.It became black in 1 second) Here is where the story begins.
After that it all became horrible.Started seeing disgusting faces.I saw my friend like a 70 year old guy.His hands were morphing into an alien hand with horribly long fingers.Our faces were morphing into weird shapes.He said he couldnt see my pupils at all.Only white blank eyes staring to him.Sometimes he wouldnt even see a face just blank skin.The same happened to me but his pupils were alright.His eyes could move in every direction 360 degrees !


We both saw my cat sleeping on the bed.When we moved closer it morphed into a blanket.
Saw red giant spiders walking on the roof of my neighbors house.
All this stuff lasted until 5-6 am.Besides all the psychedelic effects it had really bad effects physically too.
Our skin was quiet yellow.It felt like a lizard;s skin.It felt like it was being stretched.
My friends left eye was disoriented.What i mean is basically the both eyes were not at the same level.The left eye was little bit more down.
Around 8 am i started having panic attacks and hypothermia.My hands and feet were in dark purple color.They were starting to get numb every second i let them relax.After sometime it all became serious and i felt the need to go to the hospital.But somehow my friend convinced me to stay home and relax.I massaged my hands and it was getting better.Basically what i think is, my veins were contracted a lot and because of that, the blood flow was quiet low and it was getting really numb.
My friend felt great at that time.The effects were still active at 10 am.We were complaining about the effects and when would it end.Theres a lot more to the story but these are the main things that happened that day.

I would rate the pink pills 9/10.No Jaw clenching.It was hot outside,even without the pill we were sweating so,cant blame the pill.Felt really euphoric.Music was great.Everything was perfect until we f***ed up.
As i said,the pills were fantastic.According to seller they were over 200mg.Hope this info helps !
description:
Went dark purple to black in under 2 seconds.(Marquis test)
It was MDMA/MDA.I experienced heavy hallucinations because of higher doses.
Also,sorry for the picture quality.

Hi guys. This is my 2nd report on this portal and unfortunately again it's about bad trip :D When the topic is bad trip, I like talking so that's why the report is long. You may not want to read all of them :)

My friends got these pills from KuruÃ§ay's famous dealer. Before I talk about the pills I wanna talk about my condition. I and my close friends went to Bodrum for a some kind college festival/holiday last thursday. So I was on the hotel till the saturday (the day I consumed pills). There was free/unlimited alcohol at hotel and we had lotssss offf weed. All we did from thursday to saturday was drinking alcohol, smoking weed and swimming in the pool in the daytime and going the night clubs at nights. I slept barely 5-6 hours a day and saturday night I was already high on alcohol and weed, tired, sleepy and kinda sick because of bad weather.

I and my 2 friends roll the pills at midnight just before the enter the night club. I rolled 2 superman at once my friends rolled 1 queen. The night club is famous night club but it is really shit for us. (Music, other people etc) But we had to be there because our other friends were there( they didnt take any pills) After 30 minutes nothing happened. I called my another friend and tell him "come and pick us, this place is shit" We were waiting him at outside and this part was really good. Lots of different musics from different bars/clubs made me so nice. My friend came and took us, in the car we played our favorite musics and that part was also awesome. My friends were also having a great time in the car.

We went to hotel room. We had quite big weed stash only for this night and we smoked so much weed. The conversation was so nice but had no desire to music or dancing. That made me sad because even on sober, I like dancing and music. After few hours, our other friends came back from club and suddenly there was 7-8 people in the room. I liked the situation because everywhere I looked, I saw my lovely friends but there was no europhia at all. Weird isn't it?

But little bit after, bad trips started. Now when the person in front of me talk, I heard his voice from the back. I saw the person next to me on the air. OK, these trips are not unusual of course, I lived these many times. For example 2 months ago I rolled 5 white facebook and in the end of the night I lived these trips but It wasn't scary at all and I was so happy, on euphoria. This time I wasnt on euphoria and I only rolled 2 pills. 

Because of I felt bad I told my other friends (who took different pills. they were so happy, they were dancing etc.) lets go to the hotel's lobby and get some alcohol. We got some drinks and stayed at the lobby. Suddenly I realized that my friends were looking at me and say something. I understand nothing and reply like "what? sorry?" Then I heard "You're smart kid, come on, dont be like that, get rid off this trip" etc. Finally I get of this trip and they said I acted so weird and got flush too much. And they said they spoke to me about 2-3 minutes but gave no reaction to their talks until last few words. 

We got few more drinks and got back to our room. We had 3 more blue superman. I wasnt sure to take it but I took it anyway :D My friends also took those supermans (Later they said "quuen was awesome pills but supermans are not it's bad, not clean and gave us anxiety). We continue to smoke weed and talking. I dont remember those parts but I was awake. Around 9.30pm, our door knocked and a friend came in and said "come on, lets have a breakfast" I had a breakfast, I had my breakfast without difficulty. 2 hours later I ate lunch without difficulty, again. 

All in all, I didnt like the pills. Made me talk too much (which I really like), good touching sensation but no euphoria no desire to dance or music or anything. I dont use superman again. But like I said in the beginning, I was so high on alcohol and weed already, too tired, sleepy and sick. If I were healthy feelings would be better I guess.

user_report:
I consumed this pill a couple of months ago and i have never seen them again since then. I added the info because there is suspected contents in it and may not be pleasant if you are more inclined to bad trips. If you come across these, I suggest you not to buy them to prevent any possible unwanted effect. I couldn't find a chance to test them but i suspect that it may contain lsd because all the effects of it were the same with acid for the first 1-2 hours.

After 15 minutes the visuals began to change. The colors of the objects around me were darkened and became extremely sharp. All the movements around me were waving, they looked slow at first but then they became extremely fast for the next couple of hours and it really bothered me when i saw everything in lightspeeed with intensive waving. On the other hand the time felt extraordinary slow. I waited for the hit during the next 10 minutes with anxiety and i thought that it lasted for 2 hours, not 10 minutes. One of my friends who didnt use anything on that night told me that only a couple of minutes passed so i checked the clock and that moment i realised that my time perception was manipulated so im not on ex but on acid or something.

This bad experience took about an hour (in real time, not according to my perception :)) then it began to hit. I became extremely energetic and talkative. I sweated a lot. Touching sensation was great. But still time to time i saw that weird visuals just for a second. MDMA effect lasted for about 3 hours. 

Ä° had not experienced paranoia, anxiety, anger or this kind of disruption of visuals on any other pills before, that's why i am sure that this pill was not clean. I checked the other reports from other countries for bitcoin pills but the effects are not the same and they look different than this (mine has an infinity symbol next to the bitcoin logo). user_report:
Last week, I took only one pill from these. It took about an hour to hit. My eyes were extremely wiggling during the first half an hour but then it stopped suddenly. I didn't feel any extraordinary pleasure on touching or music. It is definitely not speed, even though euphoria was also slight and not continuous during the peak. I smoked pot during the entire night but there is no good or bright visuals at all. That slight euphoria stopped permanently after two hours. Although I was not physically active on that night I felt exhausted when the effects of the pill disappeared. I slept well on that night and woke up quite early on the other day. There was almost no hangover feeling on me. There were also three more people who took the same pill with me that night and they also agreed that the pill was quite weak. Only one of them experienced nausea during the roll.

I love the way how ecstasy heighten my perceptions and senses but these pills are not good on these at all.

00:45 - joint smoked, somewhat amplified the pill but still so weak effects

01:30 - effects completely worn-off, transition to good old "weed high"

01:50 - went to bed and fall asleep instantly. no surprise. and no hangover in the morning, it was like we havent rolled.

All we need from you is to post in English whenever possible, all non relevant comments posted in Turkish will be removed and this is to cut down on the dealing, sourcing that is happening in this section.

name: Grenade
user_report:
Link to picture of pills: http://s3.postimg.org/kkquhjphv/20150724_182848.jpg

I bought two of these Grenades and went to a Colour Festival. I took 1 and a half at first, waited an hour, and took the other half. 

T+00:00
Take the first dose, 1 and 1/2
T+01:00
Take Second dose, 1/2 pill
T+01:30
I am full of energy as my body falls into a euphoric state. My heart also begins to beat faster and my body temperature rises a bit. I danced on the dance floot for around 30 minutes before I felt the real urge to drink water. 
T+02:00
The line to get water was packed, as so many people were on x and needed water desperately. I began feeling sudden rushes of heat, but I was lucky because I was close to the front. A man in front of me offered to get water for me. I agreed and gave him the money. I immediately noticed that my tactile sense has changed. The old 20,000 Livra bill I was holding felt very soft like silk. This is when I really noticed that I was tripping.
T+02:30
I walk to the back of the concert where many people are laying down in the rocks. As I look around I begin to feel a very strange attraction. That is when I realised that everyone was on E. I could tell as they all exhibited the same symptoms as myself, jaw clenching, dilated pupils, and the lost look on their faces. It was incredible to find so many people on E. I began talking to different people, and I found myself being better able to communicate. A group wanted to go dance, so I went with them. 
T+03:00
With the excitement provided by all the different lights and the music that was being played, I was dancing like I have never danced in my life. Foot stomping is my personal favourite, esepecially when the song being played is repetitive. I actually ended up dancing like this for around 5 more hours. It was awesome.
T+08:00
The effects of the pill have almost worn off. I still feel my jaws clenching, and I still have that lost look on my face. I have no appetite, and I just want to go back home ans smoke some hashish and go to bed. 

Overall, this Grenade was a great experience. I recommend it to anyone who loves to dance for long hours.

name: Li-ion+
user_report:
these were the only pills my seller has for a while.
i liked it first time and second, then got 6 of them for my birthday.

first night i dropped one pill. after 2,5 hours i started feeling down and dropped another. it lasted 1,5 hours.
i was going on with some good weed, actively thinking about stuff and writing things so i didn't sleep.
the following day (probably at 4:00PM) i went out to take my girlfriend. i'm not sure i was feeling terrible or just excited.
we dropped one each. i was sleepless, so i think the pill includes amphetamine. i felt the fucking euphoria for only 15 minutes. my girlfriend was feeling amazing and thanking me. i was like "yeah (fuck everything)...".
i slept 4 or 5 hours and woke up during night, started waiting for the fucking sun.
in the morning, we dropped one each again. fuck it. that felt like a damn antidepressant. she felt good about first 30 minutes, but then she felt like throwing up. so we went out for a walk. i said "i'm walking on the emptiness". the buildings around us was looking like frames of photographs unreally taken.
there was no weed left so fuck it. it was terrible guys.
6 hours later (probably at 3:00 PM) the fatigue and bad feelings started to disappear.
i was okay with speed and that's it.

i do not recommend the pill.

Euphoria: 10/10

These pills contain pure captagon and sold as ecstasy. Please be careful when you drop these. You can feel the euphoric effects from the pills in 30 mins.

Becareful, this is not mdma.

What is Captagon? - Short Info - my researches about captagon

Captagon is brand name of lab which first captagon aka phenylethylline synthesized.

Captagon is a prodrug. Human body metabolize as it amphetamine and theophyline. Also it is powerful form of Cocaine. 

Captagon textured tablets usually contain captagon but sometimes it is not...
You can easily understand the diffence via press. 

But captagon causes severe health problems like heart attack, cardiovascular intoxication and more symptoms like these...

*** Withdrawal symptoms are very similar to cocaine. 

*** It is very harmful as you can see please stay away from these. ***

We had two of these pills. At 7.00 pm we dropped a half and a quad at the same time. 
At 7.45 Butterflies in stomach feeling, body euphoria, jaw clenching, teeth grinding, dilated pupils. Appreciation of music. Feelings of love. All of them continued about 3h.

At 8.30 we smoked well prepared amount of weed(high thc content over 20%)to aggravate visuals.

At 9.20 we smoked again without reason. 

At 9.40 we dropped the last quad of our pills.


Between 10pm - 2am: we reached psychedelic level 2. At the end melting and true hallucinations occured. (at 10.15 pm)Under low brightining room, we started to see multiple color shifts on surfaces and paraidolias.

Great night! Total trip duration: 6-8 hours / Hangover: feel good with some short-term memory problems. ( we couldnt roll for a month ( Old tolerance is around 250-270mg ))

21:45 İngested 1
23:00 Smooth come up with warmness and ticklings on my back expanding throughout my whole body.pupils are dilated.tactile sensation enhancing with music appreciation.the first effects were very similar to diamond series that were going around the last summer so that made me think these are from the same successors

I wasn't using more than 1 year, a friend of mine said "blue dolphins" and my mind is blown because i thought they were old "blue dolphins" they were really strong, speedy and clean pills.

I decided to consume, i couldn't resist...big mistake really a biiigg mistake. I'm so angry to producers of these pills. I hope they die.

We decided to take at a club, but my friend couldn't hide his pills good enough so security found and said "you shall not pass" (lol)

We took one, nothing happened after 1 hour. we decided to take second pills, we were nearly passed out. we didn't have energy to lift our heads. I laid on bed, i was high, a different high that i didn't experienced before. first time in my life i didn't want to talk, dance, move etc. we were much more sober after about 2 hours.

I haven't tried heroin but i suspect heroin, because i havent heard a pill that makes you lazy, fainted etc.

Stay away from these pills.

name: White Yin Yang
user_report:
These pills are sold as ecstasy. If you are expecting MDMA, you might get disappointed.

01:00 Consumed first pill
01:45 Something is coming !
02:00 Holy sh*t ! I was high but i realized it wasn't MDMA. I felt like butterfly of love ( it is an expression in my country, i don't know is there a word or phrase in English for that) I had desire to dance but i was so happy on sofa. So i decided to enjoy the music and conversation while lying down. I want to rename this pill as "oh my gosh pill". One of the girls said "oh my god" 456354675467 times for 3 hours ! 

These pills genarates strong desire for sex. Does not cause erectile disfunction lol.

I consumed only 1 pill but i was high for 5 hours ! I felt a mild headache at comedown. I was able to eat at 08:00am. In my mdma experiences i had to wait at least 15-16 hours to eat.

Turkish : 

Bu haplar ecstasy olarak satılıyor. Eğer alırken MDMA bekliyorsanız hayal kırıklığına uğrayabilirsiniz, içeriği MDA. Ev ortamı dışında rahatsızlık verebilir.

01:00 Birinci hapı aldım.
01:45 Bir şeyler geliyor ama dur bakalım.
02:00 Oha ! Kafam güzel ama bu kesinlikle MDMA değil. Sevgi kelebeğine döndüm. Dans etme isteğim vardı ama kanepede uzanıp müziğin ve muhabbetin tadını çıkarmak daha çok işime geldi. Daha önce MDA denk gelmemiş birisini izlemek oldukça eğlenceli olabiliyor, saatlerce yaşadıklarına inanamayıp "eyvah eyvah", "allahım" diye kendi kendine konuşup gülme krizlerine girebiliyor. Bu hapın adını "eyvah eyvah" koymak lazım.

Bu haplar seks için inanılmaz bir istek yaratıyor. Ereksiyon problemi olmuyor :)

Sadece 1 hap aldım ama etkisi 5 saat sürdü, düşüşte hafif bir başağrısı yaptı. Sabah 8 de iştahla kahvaltı edebildim, MDMA olsaydı 15-16 saat bir şey koyamazdım ağzıma.

Not : 

Birinci tekil şahış = Sokakta tanıştığım adını hatırlamadığım birisi.
Diğer karakterler = Hayali arkadaşlarım.

Uyarı : uyuşturu ve uyarıcı maddelerin kullanımı kanunen suçtur. Kalp krizi, böbrek yetmezliği, hafıza problemleri gibi bir çok tehlikesi vardır. Kullanmayın, kullandırtmayın. Bu rapor kendisini riske atanların bir nebze daha güvende olması için yazılmıştır.
